    dc:creator "Harvey, Michael B.; Hamidy, Amir; Kurniawan, Nia; Shaney, Kyle; Smith, Eric N." ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Three new species of Pseudocalotes (Squamata: Agamidae) from southern Sumatra, Indonesia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252336>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252334>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252331> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252336>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Holotype of Pseudocalotes rhammanotus (MZB 10804, SVL 67.9 mm) from montane forest above Danau Ranau, Lampung, Sumatra." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/252336/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252334>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Cephalic morphology of Pseudocalotes guttalineatus (A, UTA 60554, head length 20.7 mm) and P. rhammanotus (B, MZB 10804, head length 15.2 mm). Heavily keeled scales of dorsolateral series, similar antehumeral scale, and depressed area ventral and posterior to antehumeral fold shaded gray." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/252334/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252331>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Gular region of Pseudocalotes cybelidermus (A, UTA 60551, head width 7.3 mm), P. guttalineatus (B, UTA 60500, head width 8.1 mm), and P. rhammanotus (C, MZB 10804, head width 10.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/252331/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

